# Cybersecurity is Everywhere

<div style="background-color: #a6e3e8; border-radius: 40px; color: #000000; width: 95%; padding: 1px 20px 1px 20px;">

<p style="line-height: 1.5; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; "><strong>Teacher Tip:</strong> Cybersecurity plays a crucial role in various industries, from healthcare to transportation. Helping students connect these real-world applications to cybersecurity principles enhances their understanding of digital security, privacy, and risk management.
</p>
</div>

<br>


<table style="width:100%; text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"> <tr> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/c063cc1809e98ebc07d0659bb8dc52c8-image-1724079338929.png" alt="Healthcare Icon" style="width:75px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/4d6957c590afe4356a34fd0d880dada9-image-1724079415496.png" alt="Finance Icon" style="width:70px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/febd63b16d05af08c0c69b6f2b76fb09-image-1724079744724.png" alt="Transportation Icon" style="width:75px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> </tr> </table> <table border="1" style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:14pt; table-layout:fixed; margin-bottom:30px;"> <tr style="background-color:#f0f0f0;"> <th>Healthcare</th> <th>Finance</th> <th>Transportation</th> </tr> <tr> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Protecting patient records from cyber threats</li> <li>Securing medical devices from hacking</li> <li>Ensuring data privacy in telemedicine services</li> </ul> </td> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Preventing fraud through advanced security systems</li> <li>Encrypting online transactions</li> <li>Safeguarding financial institutions from cyberattacks</li> </ul> </td> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Securing GPS navigation systems</li> <li>Protecting ride-sharing and public transit platforms</li> <li>Ensuring safe communication between smart vehicles</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </table> <table style="width:100%; text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"> <tr> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/24815a5ef848a7ae17799879e481847f-image-1724079815627.png" alt="Education Icon" style="width:75px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/fe851509654f7a2f909715868a3d7fde-image-1724079637108.png" alt="Retail Icon" style="width:75px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> <td style="width:33%;"> <img src="https://images.code.org/a93502230072c87cd257ac2516e45e91-image-1724080036483.png" alt="Environmental Icon" style="width:75px; border-radius:10px;"> </td> </tr> </table> <table border="1" style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:14pt; table-layout:fixed;"> <tr style="background-color:#f0f0f0;"> <th>Education</th> <th>Retail</th> <th>Environmental Science</th> </tr> <tr> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Implementing secure online learning environments</li> <li>Preventing cyberbullying and phishing attacks</li> <li>Protecting student data from unauthorized access</li> </ul> </td> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Protecting customer data from breaches</li> <li>Securing e-commerce transactions</li> <li>Preventing cyber fraud in digital payment systems</li> </ul> </td> <td style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:top; padding:10px;"> <ul> <li>Safeguarding data from environmental monitoring systems</li> <li>Securing smart grids from cyber threats</li> <li>Ensuring the integrity of climate research data</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </table>
